{
  "stem": "23572.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But in those days, I think, they, they stopped at age 15.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Anything below age 15, they-- in those days, they didn't take them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But other people, they just took them and, you know-- And so the youth aliyah-- the-- so my mother inquired.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they said, we'll take one of your boys.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We were trying to reach-- trying to reach Palestine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So I was one-- I was one of the boys.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "My wife-- my thought, you know, at least get me out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And then, I said, you know, I'll try and get you out afterwards.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And so my mother signed me up for this-- for this transport to go to Vienna.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I think in the Jewish community, somehow, we had some money.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But the youth aliyah-- Rechaa Freier was one of the sponsors of this thing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, Recha-- R-E-C-H-A-A-A, F-R-E-I-E-R-- Freier.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And people in Hadassah-- I think she was one of the disciples of Henrietta Szold of Hadassah.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anybody with youth aliyah, this is a revered name, Rechaa Freier.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, before I know, I was-- I remember the night my mother took me to the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was, was dark.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was dark, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I cried.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I, I, I, I-- like I knew it's the last time I'm going to see her.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was only-- I was only, what, 13, 14 years old.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was never bar mitzvahed in-- I was never bar mitzvahed, by the way.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I'll come to that [LAUGHS]-- I'll come to that later on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And, and we took-- we went to-- we went to the train.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she turned me over to one of the leaders, which I don't know who they are.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I have no recollection whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I just know I bitterly cried, all the way to the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
